Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.00,0:00:10.51,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的告白 竟然被接受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.30,0:00:14.13,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 我們交往吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.30,0:00:18.64,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有些無法釋然呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.97,0:00:23.73,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種巨乳又可愛的辣妹怎麼可能會和我交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.94,0:00:25.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用常識思考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.35,0:00:29.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是先讓我放松警惕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.11,0:00:31.94,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把我的醜態散布到全校讓我成為眾矢之的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.49,0:00:36.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼多疑可不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.49,0:00:39.08,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼不能相信八女同學呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.08,0:00:41.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在可是八女同學的男朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.45,0:00:45.12,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說些什麼純情又蠢的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.46,0:00:47.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辣妹可是很可怕的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.42,0:00:51.59,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是和我們不同的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.59,0:00:55.93,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有那種思想我們才是童貞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.09,0:00:59.43,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受夠你的漂亮話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.09,0:01:00.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}暴力反對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.49,0:01:17.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說麻煩的話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.95,0:01:22.24,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的只要能和那個色色的辣妹睡就好了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.83,0:01:27.08,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.62,0:01:30.17,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還認真的聽課來著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.63,0:01:32.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不好吧 八女同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.67,0:01:34.17,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.01,0:01:36.47,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.01,0:01:39.26,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來不就是要做「不好」的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.51,0:01:41.68,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不好的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.22,0:01:44.89,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是啰嗦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.77,0:01:52.57,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的事 等我們做完再去想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.40,0:01:54.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等做完再想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.24,0:01:57.07,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.00,0:03:32.30,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(880,640)\fad(300,300)}第2話  第一次的卡拉OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.30,0:03:32.59,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}雖然昨晚的妄想裡很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.72,0:03:35.05,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是實際上到底該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.43,0:03:40.02,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話我完全沒有在和那麼可愛的辣妹交往的實感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.27,0:03:42.52,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說在告白的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.98,0:03:45.90,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也是那麼開心的在欺負我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.98,0:03:50.57,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不要再和她扯上關系比較好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.65,0:03:51.19,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.90,0:03:52.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.78,0:03:54.91,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 是你們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.28,0:03:57.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.62,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了 純一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.25,0:04:02.29,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們做的有些過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.79,0:04:08.84,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來是這群家伙逼我去告白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.09,0:04:10.63,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不管那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.76,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.76,0:04:14.43,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是被那個辣妹做了很過分的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.68,0:04:15.97,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會給你建議的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.43,0:04:21.02,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實因為昨天的事被八女同學盯上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.35,0:04:24.23,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的高中生活要被搞的亂七八糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.10,0:04:25.85,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然這麼慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.86,0:04:30.82,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這之後要怎麼辦才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.65,0:04:32.99,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.82,0:04:38.24,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你被那個辣妹傳出什麼傳聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.41,0:04:41.74,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你被那群現充做了多麼過分的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.00,0:04:45.16,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都會幫助純一的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.33,0:04:48.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們永遠是朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.96,0:04:50.92,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.50,0:04:54.97,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 我不是還有這群家伙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.34,0:04:57.47,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要傷心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.89,0:05:00.14,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人已經夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.85,0:05:03.39,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 有個信息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.81,0:05:09.90,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自拍照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.19,0:05:12.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 昨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.44,0:05:13.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.19,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.36,0:05:18.03,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這是我的聯絡方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.74,0:05:23.62,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋 擅自被交換聯絡方式了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.79,0:05:25.41,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.60,0:05:41.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(828,304)\fad(300,0)}非現充
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.85,0:05:41.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1099,186)\fad(300,0)}沒朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.80,0:05:41.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(164,186)\fad(300,0)}宅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.05,0:05:41.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(364,641)\fad(300,0)}童貞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.54,0:05:26.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.75,0:05:29.13,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現充會傳染的 能別和我們說話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.17,0:05:31.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你這種幸福混蛋根本就不是朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.67,0:05:32.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說我恨你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.92,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這種不合理的事 我都快氣瘋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.30,0:05:37.05,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學有妹妹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.05,0:05:41.47,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不奢侈的 有小學四年級到五年級就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.06,0:05:45.06,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的手掌翻的真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.93,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手腕真柔軟呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.10,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是白擔心你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.52,0:05:55.74,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊...並不是你們想的那樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.99,0:05:57.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.16,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經接吻了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.74,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才一天啊 怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.74,0:06:04.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.04,0:06:07.41,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 純一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.58,0:06:10.21,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對辣妹而言接吻只不過是打招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.46,0:06:12.34,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是關系好的男生的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.34,0:06:15.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻就如同呼吸一般平常的東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.46,0:06:17.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.84,0:06:20.09,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 接吻是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.97,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子會不會喜歡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.22,0:06:24.97,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此 畢竟八女同學是個辣妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.10,0:06:27.18,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻的難度應該會下降很多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.35,0:06:30.73,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 假設說那個回復是真的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.02,0:06:35.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得好嗎 純一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.44,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八...八女同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.24,0:06:39.95,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是早安的吻喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.32,0:06:45.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我接下來可以吻到爽嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.70,0:06:47.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.54,0:06:50.00,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你已經明白了呢 純一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.25,0:06:53.29,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 凡事都有個先後順序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.46,0:06:56.80,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究還是要循序漸進才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.51,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 師父大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.38,0:07:01.47,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就傳授你精髓所在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.39,0:07:09.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一啊 邀請她去卡拉OK吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.06,0:07:13.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...為什麼是卡拉OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.31,0:07:20.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這群童貞啊 所以說你們才一直是童貞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.11,0:07:21.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.11,0:07:22.66,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了童貞們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.99,0:07:27.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現充們是會把卡拉OK當成賓館用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.66,0:07:34.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是從卡拉OK打工的經驗中得到的准確情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.13,0:07:39.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我從中發現了堪比諾貝爾獎的法則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.05,0:07:41.01,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.97,0:07:50.77,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉OK的xx法則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.77,0:07:54.52,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉OK的xx法則...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.27,0:07:57.44,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遜爆了這名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.65,0:07:58.65,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拙建而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.45,0:08:04.41,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱一些有點色色歌詞的歌曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.12,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用合唱炒熱氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.12,0:08:07.87,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生脫衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.87,0:08:11.87,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要集齊這三點 那這對情侶就一定會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.75,0:08:13.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對情侶就會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.42,0:08:17.46,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會搞起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.75,0:08:18.96,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.09,0:08:25.13,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.76,0:08:33.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉OK是去唱歌的地方啊 才不是啪啪啪的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是...啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.48,0:08:37.61,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 撐住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.52,0:08:42.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要辜負我的犧牲 純一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.65,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會犧牲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.24,0:08:46.41,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去邀請那個辣妹去卡拉OK吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.70,0:08:49.78,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就可以在接吻的同時童貞畢業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.41,0:08:51.33,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.58,0:08:56.92,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎平 慎平!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.92,0:08:58.29,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,let's kiss
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.46,0:09:04.84,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉OK嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.09,0:09:07.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題就在於該怎麼邀請啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.55,0:09:09.39,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 羽柴君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.76,0:09:11.10,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香椎同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.68,0:09:15.02,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎 一大早就一臉復雜的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.02,0:09:16.44,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼煩心事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.44,0:09:19.06,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事 沒什麼事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.06,0:09:20.77,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.82,0:09:24.03,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 也可以找我商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.15,0:09:27.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 不過真的沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.78,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你擔心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.95,0:09:33.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了跟辣妹啪 而在煩惱怎麼邀請她去卡拉OK什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.58,0:09:36.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要多厚顏無恥才能找香椎同學談這種事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 純一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.58,0:09:40.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸...安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.17,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好柔軟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.75,0:09:45.84,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上發給你的自拍看了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.51,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當興奮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.80,0:09:50.97,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...嗯 很可愛的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.97,0:09:54.22,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 我都沒用美圖喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.64,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.85,0:10:01.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學和羽柴君關系有這麼好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.11,0:10:07.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和純一從昨天開始交往了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.41,0:10:12.03,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.67,0:10:21.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早真是災難啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.54,0:10:24.92,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還被很多平時都不怎麼說話的人搭話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.42,0:10:28.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是邀請八女同學去卡拉OK的氛圍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.63,0:10:33.47,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從早上到現在 八女同學就一直在回答朋友的提問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.68,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半點搭話的機會都沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.68,0:10:39.94,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我也要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.44,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.60,0:10:42.90,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.03,0:10:52.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼回事啊 稍微等等我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.49,0:10:57.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友君你不是有著可愛的女朋友麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該跟我們這些童貞沒什麼話好說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.29,0:11:05.00,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾你現充 祝你在痛苦中爆炸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.17,0:11:08.71,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一 你有問八女同學她有沒有妹妹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.76,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好冷淡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.93,0:11:13.68,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反而是最震驚的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.68,0:11:14.64,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.05,0:11:17.68,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道細節 但你實在是太令人羨慕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.68,0:11:21.44,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太胡扯了 還不是你們強迫我告白的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.44,0:11:23.73,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想聽大道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.27,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然走掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.27,0:11:28.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群自作主張的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.61,0:11:33.61,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.87,0:11:37.66,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一 你放學後反正很閑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.12,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微陪我下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.29,0:11:46.46,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙啊 回家吧 青蛙啊 回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.30,0:11:49.76,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 八女同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.26,0:11:52.68,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 純一閉嘴跟我來就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.64,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥 哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.39,0:11:59.47,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寧音?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.48,0:12:04.23,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為什麼牽著手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.52,0:12:05.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.60,0:12:08.73,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在交往啊 牽個手很正常吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.36,0:12:16.49,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你個木腦殼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.16,0:12:19.24,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是純一的妹妹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.54,0:12:21.79,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的好可愛呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.79,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,類似妹妹一樣的存在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.17,0:12:28.21,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說了 趕緊走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.59,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.59,0:12:31.71,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.63,0:12:35.51,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大聲地叫喊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.76,0:12:39.10,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且能夠令人身心偷快的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.35,0:12:41.89,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.89,0:12:43.85,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.06,0:12:45.02,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.94,0:12:47.73,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先一個小時吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.44,0:12:51.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 卡拉OK啊 我還以為是賓館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.61,0:12:52.86,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.99,0:12:56.53,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們會拿卡拉OK當賓館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.16,0:12:58.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和計劃一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.45,0:13:04.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我只和那三個笨蛋去過卡拉OK啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.96,0:13:08.63,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就和辣妹來 我到底要唱些什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.63,0:13:11.17,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一在真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.38,0:13:13.76,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然超想唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.76,0:13:16.68,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常的一起來的人卻都有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.68,0:13:18.51,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此這麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.35,0:13:22.01,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來想和她們一起鬧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.52,0:13:25.31,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是替補啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.98,0:13:31.23,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就暫且用和純一的校服約會來充數吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.78,0:13:34.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.86,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.86,0:13:42.12,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就更加不知道該唱什麼好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.83,0:13:46.87,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\bord0\c&H000000&\fs40\pos(17,102)\u0}致客人們\N這裡是卡拉OK\N請不要做{\c&H141aa5&\u1\s0}K歌以外的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.83,0:13:46.87,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是卡拉OK請不要做K歌以外...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這這 這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.17,0:13:51.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四眼仔說的是真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.13,0:13:59.84,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貼了這告知就說明真的有那樣的情侶啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.43,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.14,0:14:05.27,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在學雞叫嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.27,0:14:06.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.89,0:14:08.23,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿果汁來了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.64,0:14:09.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.60,0:14:15.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是八女同學也不會跳過接吻直接啪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.61,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借過一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.24,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房間好窄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.04,0:14:27.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先點咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.29,0:14:30.04,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.04,0:14:31.29,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.29,0:14:32.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是在撩我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.92,0:14:35.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學的體溫透過我的手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.38,0:14:37.59,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接能感受到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.17,0:14:40.80,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下不會真的有戲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.35,0:14:45.47,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學 你要干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.52,0:14:48.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我蹭 我磨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.81,0:14:55.19,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一你已經硬邦邦了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.15,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.53,0:15:00.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放松點的話 可唱不了歌哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.91,0:15:03.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這狀態怎麼能唱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.58,0:15:07.66,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.58,0:15:14.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來給你按摩 放 松 一 下 吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.13,0:15:18.71,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸麥的手好撩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.01,0:15:25.05,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.35,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看八女同學就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.72,0:15:32.10,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱的那麼歡 純碎就是來唱歌的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.37,0:15:55.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一你不點歌嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.92,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.71,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學你先點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.13,0:16:01.76,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.34,0:16:06.51,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下不妙了 我也得唱兩首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.93,0:16:10.85,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排行榜上的歌沒首認識的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.10,0:16:13.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能唱的全都是動漫歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.48,0:16:16.19,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道辣妹喜歡的歌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.81,0:16:20.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 我只能唱不太像動漫歇的動漫歌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.28,0:16:27.05,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}我也想要啊 已經無法忍耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.05,0:16:31.65,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}「不是和誰都可以」這不是借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.65,0:16:38.15,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}犯錯的記憶 這噪音纏繞在耳邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.65,0:16:44.15,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}在我的身體印上你的印記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.15,0:16:50.15,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}我已不想再過沒有你的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.21,0:16:51.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.60,0:16:56.85,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}唱一些有點色色歌詞的歌曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.68,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我冷靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.85,0:16:57.10,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有別的深意 大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.36,0:17:00.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是我在唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.53,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純一你也點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.74,0:17:04.15,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.49,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要唱哪個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.74,0:17:10.91,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就唱夏日回憶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.83,0:17:18.63,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是動漫歌嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.13,0:17:19.79,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起唱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.84,0:17:25.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.16,0:17:52.83,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這動畫真的超懷念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.16,0:17:55.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 但是好意外啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.50,0:17:57.66,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學居然會唱動漫歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.83,0:18:02.34,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼意外的 這首歌在我們這代是必點的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.71,0:18:06.76,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是挺懂動漫歌的 純一你使勁點歌就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.55,0:18:10.47,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿嘞 難道說 八女同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.55,0:18:13.22,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在遷就我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.18,0:18:18.35,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們再來一首吧 這首你會麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.02,0:18:19.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.90,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個情況不就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.57,0:18:25.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}用合唱炒熱氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.57,0:18:25.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小一小一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.24,0:18:27.44,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.44,0:18:30.53,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能把八女同學的好意套上這麼下三濫的法則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.53,0:18:31.87,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是人嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.87,0:18:33.87,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 不覺得熱麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.24,0:18:34.99,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.50,0:18:43.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 全部點亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.38,0:18:46.55,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下只有上了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.71,0:18:49.01,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們冷靜點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.17,0:18:52.26,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些只是那個鬼畜眼鏡的一面之詞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.26,0:18:53.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.60,0:18:56.64,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對哦 再怎麼說在這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.23,0:19:05.19,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 所以你們才會是童貞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.52,0:19:08.24,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要再給淑女蒙羞嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.86,0:19:11.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 帥哥!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.03,0:19:14.74,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學她已經完全綻放了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.03,0:19:18.33,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了名為欲望的真紅薔薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.54,0:19:21.17,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時不出手還算什麼男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.87,0:19:25.21,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明哲保身可能會讓男人出局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.59,0:19:30.42,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據情況犧牲自己來回應女性才是真男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.88,0:19:31.59,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.18,0:19:37.26,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說本來就沒打算當真男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.39,0:19:42.69,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且即使男人一回也不是絕對能童貞畢業不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.02,0:19:47.15,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是八女向學她沒那個意思的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.44,0:19:48.61,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.19,0:19:54.24,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只有舉起祖傳的求愛標志的寶劍奮勇向前了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.91,0:20:00.37,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵循自己下半身的行為我不會否定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.75,0:20:04.21,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是滿足肉欲之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.88,0:20:07.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對淑女還必須要做一件事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.75,0:20:09.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.26,0:20:14.18,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然 只能是火熱的吻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.76,0:20:19.18,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忽略前戲的人是都是遠遠算不上男人的人渣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.89,0:20:23.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不想成為這樣的人渣的 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.52,0:20:28.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱吻 親嘴 接吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.52,0:20:28.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}帥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.32,0:20:31.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學 非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.53,0:20:34.99,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直沒想到你邀請我來卡拉OK是這個打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.86,0:20:36.62,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.04,0:20:44.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不上的話 不是男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.62,0:20:45.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.17,0:20:47.67,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你鼻毛露出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.59,0:20:49.38,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.71,0:20:53.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.26,0:20:56.22,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微去下厲廁所哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.85,0:21:07.56,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 接吻的目的太明顯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.06,0:21:12.23,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能...那麼輕易地就接吻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.20,0:21:19.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.53,0:21:23.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後無論做什麼都會被提到「你鼻毛露出來了」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.70,0:21:28.54,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 鼻毛 要是沒有你的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.67,0:21:33.09,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學 請原諒這樣鼻孔雜草叢生的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.63,0:21:35.13,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今到很開心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.05,0:21:39.51,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能還想和純一去卡拉OK呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.93,0:21:43.18,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.52,0:21:45.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走了啦 快站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.73,0:21:49.35,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八女同學 等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.52,0:21:50.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.36,0:21:52.11,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼鼻孔有點疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.66,0:23:26.99,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙好 我是步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.99,0:23:27.74,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.74,0:23:30.08,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前心科普了些小知識所以今天該我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.08,0:23:31.16,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 讓我聽聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.16,0:23:34.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7)\fs35}卡拉OK:日文ラオケ 其中カオ是空的意思\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hオケ是orchestra(管弦樂)的縮略音譯 意為不帶歌手(原唱)的管弦樂(伴奏)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.16,0:23:32.58,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道為什麼卡拉OK叫卡拉OK嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.58,0:23:34.75,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是空的和管弦樂的簡稱對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.88,0:23:36.84,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼小知識什麼時候告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.84,0:23:38.30,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意的嗎!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.00,0:23:39.51,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(635,530)\fad(300,0)}下回\N第一次的黑GAL
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.30,0:23:39.51,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的小知識呢?
Comment: Marked=0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.00,0:02:13.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Like  自由なキミが好きだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.00,0:02:13.48,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like  雖然喜歡自由的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.68,0:02:18.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ほっとかれたらそれはそれでさみしい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.68,0:02:18.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果被冷落的話我會感到寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.46,0:02:23.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Love 「髪を切りすぎちゃったみたい」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.56,0:02:23.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love 「頭發好像剪得太短了」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「ほんとだ」じゃない!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不該說「是真的呢」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.92,0:02:29.24,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}そこは「でもかわいい」でしょ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.92,0:02:29.24,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是要說「剪短也可愛呀」對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.44,0:02:33.05,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}そっと目を閉じたまま
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.44,0:02:33.05,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜靜閉上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.05,0:02:35.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}指先で探した
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.05,0:02:35.50,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用指尖去觸及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.50,0:02:40.16,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}鍵と鍵穴みたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.50,0:02:40.16,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如鑰匙和鎖孔般默契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.04,0:02:43.63,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}そうだ この次のデート
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.04,0:02:43.63,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次的約會地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.64,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}わたしにまかせて!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.64,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來做決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.00,0:02:50.63,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}夏をプロデュースしたげる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.00,0:02:50.63,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個夏天制造最完美的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ふたりきりで
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.83,0:02:53.92,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You are the First One!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.83,0:02:53.92,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一個!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.92,0:02:54.41,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.92,0:02:54.41,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.99,0:02:57.76,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ついにやってきましたマブしいSEASON
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.99,0:02:57.76,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀的季節終於來臨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.00,0:02:59.43,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.00,0:02:59.43,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.15,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}熱い太陽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.15,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎熱的太陽!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.15,0:03:02.92,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}戀する気持ち もっと盛り上がってゆこう!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.15,0:03:02.92,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的心情讓我們再熱情高漲一點吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.96,0:03:04.24,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}こたえならYes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.96,0:03:04.24,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答自然是Yes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.24,0:03:04.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.24,0:03:04.98,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}yeah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.28,0:03:08.12,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}だけどカンタンだって思われたくない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.28,0:03:08.12,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我並不想被人認為太容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.16,0:03:12.72,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}はじめては 一度だけ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.16,0:03:12.72,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次只有一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大切に to you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要將自己完整地托付於你
Comment: Marked=0,0:03:14.78,0:03:16.78,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.60,0:22:03.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ヘナチョコ面に見せかけ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.60,0:22:03.32,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意裝成無能的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.32,0:22:05.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}案外やるときゃやる奴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.32,0:22:05.88,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的是個可靠的家伙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.66,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}それでもちょこっと
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.92,0:22:08.66,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又總是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.66,0:22:11.16,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}褒めれば調子に乗ってドジる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.66,0:22:11.16,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給點陽光就得意忘形弄巧成拙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.28,0:22:14.34,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ズタボロ破れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.28,0:22:14.34,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撕裂縱橫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.34,0:22:16.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}戀の傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.34,0:22:16.45,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛的傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.45,0:22:21.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}誰にも一生見せたくないけれど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.45,0:22:21.28,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明誰都不願意見到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.12,0:22:27.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}なぜだろ自然と會話してる
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.12,0:22:27.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又情不自禁地說起了話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.84,0:22:30.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}なんだろな この感覚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.84,0:22:30.36,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢 這種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.44,0:22:33.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}あたたかい この安らぎ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.44,0:22:33.20,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好溫暖 感到安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.20,0:22:35.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}なんてことナイナイ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.20,0:22:35.60,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼的才沒有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.60,0:22:38.10,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}人生は甘くない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.60,0:22:38.10,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生可不甜美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.20,0:22:43.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}さあ 跪きなさい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.20,0:22:43.40,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 跪下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.80,0:22:46.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}あたしが好きならば!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.80,0:22:46.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是喜歡我的話!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.25,0:22:47.74,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}本気でね 本気でね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.25,0:22:47.74,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦 真的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.74,0:22:50.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ハート射止めようとか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.74,0:22:50.70,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得到我的心什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.70,0:22:51.95,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}100年早い
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.70,0:22:51.95,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早100年呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.95,0:22:53.08,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ほんとはね ほんとはね
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.95,0:22:53.08,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實啊 其實啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.08,0:22:54.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}うざい程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.08,0:22:54.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個麻煩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.25,0:22:56.80,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}良いやつなんだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.25,0:22:56.80,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.80,0:22:57.25,Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yeah!
